Market Analysis and Size

Global playout automation and channel-in-a-box market is expected to grow at a healthy growth rate due to increasing adoption of playout automation software and solutions, growing technological advancements and cost reduction. The broadcasters mainly focus on playout automation solutions and channel broadcastings to reduce power consumption and save costs. Furthermore, the increasing number of channels and fierce competition to improve channel presentation enhance the market growth.

